   --soft: #eef4f7;\\n      --accent: #14677b;\\n      --warn: #9a4a17;\\n      --bad: #993333;\\n      --good: #276749;\\n    }\\n\\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\\n\\n    body {\\n      margin: 0;\\n      color: var(--ink);\\n      background: #ffffff;\\n      font: 15px/1.62 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Segoe UI\\\", sans-serif;\\n    }\\n\\n    header {\\n      padding: 34px 42px 24px;\\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      background: #f8fbfd;\\n    }\\n\\n    main {\\n      max-width: 1220px;\\n      padding: 28px 42px 56px;\\n    }\\n\\n    h1 {\\n      margin: 0 0 8px;\\n      font-size: 30px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n\\n    h2 {\\n      margin: 30px 0 12px;\\n      font-size: 22px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n\\n    h3 {\\n      margin: 20px 0 8px;\\n      font-size: 17px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n\\n    p { margin: 8px 0; }\\n\\n    code {\\n      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;\\n      background: #edf3f7;\\n      border-radius: 4px;\\n      padding: 1px 4px;\\n      font-size: 0.92em;\\n    }\\n\\n    pre {\\n      overflow-x: auto;\\n      background: #111827;\\n      color: #f7fafc;\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\n      padding: 14px 16px;\\n      font-size: 13px;\\n      line-height: 1.5;\\n    }\\n\\n    pre code {\\n      background: transparent;\\n      padding: 0;\\n      color: inherit;\\n    }\\n\\n    table {\\n      width: 100%;\\n      border-collapse: collapse;\\n      margin: 12px 0 22px;\\n      font-size: 14px;\\n    }\\n\\n    th, td {\\n      padding: 9px 10px;\\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      vertical-align: top;\\n    }\\n\\n    th {\\n      text-align: left;\\n      background: #f1f5f8;\\n      color: #24313d;\\n    }\\n\\n    ul, ol { padding-left: 22px; }\\n    li { margin: 5px 0; }\\n\\n    .meta { color: var(--muted); }\\n    .num {\\n      text-align: right;\\n      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\\n      white-space: nowrap;\\n    }\\n\\n    .cards {\\n      display: grid;\\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(190px, 1fr));\\n      gap: 12px;\\n      margin: 16px 0;\\n    }\\n\\n    .card {\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\n      background: var(--panel);\\n      padding: 14px 16px;\\n    }\\n\\n    .card span {\\n      display: block;\\n      color: var(--muted);\\n      font-size: 13px;\\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\\n    }\\n\\n    .card strong {\\n      color: var(--accent);\\n      display: block;\\n      font-size: 22px;\\n    }\\n\\n    .callout {\\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);\\n      background: var(--soft);\\n      padding: 12px 14px;\\n      margin: 12px 0 18px;\\n    }\\n\\n    .warnbox {\\n      border-left-color: var(--warn);\\n      background: #fff7ed;\\n    }\\n\\n    .badbox {\\n      border-left-color: var(--bad);\\n      background: #fff5f5;\\n    }\\n\\n    .tag {\\n      display: inline-block;\\n      border-radius: 999px;\\n      padding: 1px 8px;\\n      font-size: 12px;\\n      font-weight: 650;\\n      white-space: nowrap;\\n    }\\n\\n    .ok { color: var(--good); background: #eaf7ef; }\\n    .warn { color: var(--warn); background: #fff2df; }\\n    .bad { color: var(--bad); background: #ffe7e7; }\\n    .info { color: var(--accent); background: #e7f3f7; }\\n\\n    @media (max-width: 860px) {\\n      header, main {\\n        padding-left: 20px;\\n        padding-right: 20px;\\n      }\\n      table {\\n        display: block;\\n        overflow-x: auto;\\n        white-space: nowrap;\\n      }\\n    }\\n  </style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n  <header>\\n    <h1>Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</h1>\\n    <p class=\\\"meta\\\">日期：2026-05-24；目标：让 Body-Tell 在结构和权重语义上尽量对齐 VoxTell v1.1，优先支持 VoxTell checkpoint 复用，而不是只做到 tensor shape 能加载。</p>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <main>\\n    <section>\\n      <h2>核验结论</h2>\\n      <div class=\\\"callout\\\">\\n        <p><strong>原差异报告中的核心不一致真实存在。</strong> 其中最影响 VoxTell 权重复用的是两类问题：一类是参数量和模块拓扑明显不同，例如 encoder/decoder；另一类是参数 shape 一致但 forward 语义不同，例如 transformer decoder。</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"cards\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>Body-Tell 当前参数</span><strong>328.98M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>VoxTell v1.1 参数</span><strong>440.03M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>Body encoder</span><strong>8.49M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>VoxTell encoder</span><strong>90.30M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>Transformer 参数</span><strong>251.86M</strong></div>\\n        <div class=\\\"card\\\"><span>最高风险</span><strong>shape 同而语义不同</strong></div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <table>\\n        <thead>\\n          <tr><th>差异点</th><th>核验结果</th><th>对权重复用的影响</th><th>证据位置</th></tr>\\n        </thead>\\n        <tbody>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Transformer decoder</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 使用 <code>activation=\\\"gelu\\\"</code>，pre-norm path 执行 self-attention；VoxTell 默认 <code>relu</code>，active <code>forward_pre</code> 跳过 self-attention，只做 cross-attention 和 FFN。</td>\\n            <td>参数名和 shape 可 100% 对上，但加载 VoxTell 权重后语义不等价。小模型同权重实验输出最大绝对差为 <code>0.9258</code>。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:69</code>、<code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:137</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:224</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Encoder backbone</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 5-stage 手写 ConvBlock；VoxTell 是 6-stage <code>ResidualEncoder</code>，features 为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320,320]</code>，blocks 为 <code>[1,3,4,6,6,6]</code>。</td>\\n            <td>当前 encoder 无法复用 VoxTell encoder 权重，也很可能限制性能上限。这个差异不是“轻量配置”，而是 backbone 类型不同。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:155</code>、<code>VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1/plans.json:20</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:131</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Mask projections（含 <code>num_heads</code>）</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> 两层根因：(1) Body-Tell 配置写 5，但运行时被 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code> 截成 4 级；(2) Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）vs VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell_model.py:74</code>）。两者乘积决定实际 projection 输出。</td>\\n            <td>Body-Tell 实际输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>（<code>channels × 32</code>，stage 0 例外）；VoxTell 实际输出 <strong><code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级</strong>（<code>channels × 1</code>）。<strong>原报告写 VoxTell 最高级 <code>10240</code> 是错误的。</strong> 即使 encoder 升到 6 级、stage 截断消除，<code>num_heads</code> 不同会导致 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与下游 mask fusion 模块的 shape 不匹配，权重无法直接复用。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>、<code>:83</code>、<code>:89</code>；<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:74</code>、<code>:177</code>、<code>:370</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Decoder</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 4-stage 手写 decoder，<code>GroupNorm + GELU</code>；VoxTell 是 5-stage <code>VoxTellDecoder</code>，使用 <code>StackedConvBlocks</code> 并继承 encoder 的 <code>InstanceNorm3d + LeakyReLU + conv_bias=true</code>。</td>\\n            <td>当前 decoder 无法复用 VoxTell decoder 权重。VoxTell 还总是构造 <code>seg_layers</code>，用于 checkpoint 兼容。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:174</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:280</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td>Position / memory 排列</td>\\n            <td><span class=\\\"tag warn\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 动态生成 <code>D,H,W</code> 顺序的位置编码；VoxTell 使用 init 时固定的 <code>pos_embed</code> buffer，并用 <code>H,W,D</code> 顺序 flatten。</td>\\n            <td>Body-Tell 当前 <code>volume_size=[129,108,256]</code>（见 <code>configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml:25</code>，2026-05-24 commit <code>5c31e57</code> 后裁剪到此尺寸）不是 192³，直接加载 VoxTell <code>pos_embed</code> 会遇到 shape/语义问题。需要明确动态重建或改成 192³ profile。</td>\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:118</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:185</code>、<code>:229</code></td>\\n          </tr>\\n        </tbody>\\n      </table>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <section>\\n      <h2>目标状态</h2>\\n      <p>新增一个 VoxTell-aligned 架构路径，而不是在现有轻量模型上做零散补丁。该路径的 state dict 命名应尽量贴近 VoxTell，降低权重加载映射复杂度。</p>\\n\\n      <table>\\n        <thead>\\n          <tr><th>模块</th><th>目标实现</th><th>权重复用要求</th></tr>\\n        </thead>\\n        <tbody>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>encoder</code></td>\\n            <td>使用 <code>dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.residual_encoders.ResidualEncoder</code>，参数与 VoxTell v1.1 plan 一致。</td>\\n            <td>加载 VoxTell <code>encoder.*</code> 权重，shape mismatch 必须报错。</td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td><code>decoder</code></td>\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_2\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,220p' Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"<!doctype html>\\n<html lang=\\\"zh-CN\\\">\\n<head>\\n  <meta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\">\\n  <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\\\">\\n  <title>Body-Tell 与 VoxTell 论文不一致项总控计划</title>\\n  <style>\\n    :root {\\n      --bg: #f6f7f9;\\n      --panel: #ffffff;\\n      --ink: #172033;\\n      --muted: #5c6678;\\n      --line: #d9dee8;\\n      --head: #eef2f7;\\n      --code: #f1f4f8;\\n      --red: #b3261e;\\n      --amber: #8a5a00;\\n      --green: #187044;\\n      --blue: #2459a8;\\n    }\\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\\n    body {\\n      margin: 0;\\n      background: var(--bg);\\n      color: var(--ink);\\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Segoe UI\\\", \\\"Noto Sans CJK SC\\\", \\\"Microsoft YaHei\\\", sans-serif;\\n      line-height: 1.62;\\n    }\\n    main {\\n      max-width: 1180px;\\n      margin: 0 auto;\\n      padding: 36px 24px 60px;\\n    }\\n    header {\\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      padding-bottom: 22px;\\n      margin-bottom: 22px;\\n    }\\n    h1 {\\n      margin: 0 0 8px;\\n      font-size: 30px;\\n      line-height: 1.25;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n    h2 {\\n      margin: 0 0 14px;\\n      font-size: 20px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n    h3 {\\n      margin: 18px 0 8px;\\n      font-size: 16px;\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\n    }\\n    p { margin: 8px 0; }\\n    section {\\n      background: var(--panel);\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\n      padding: 22px;\\n      margin: 18px 0;\\n    }\\n    table {\\n      width: 100%;\\n      border-collapse: collapse;\\n      margin: 10px 0 2px;\\n      font-size: 14px;\\n    }\\n    th, td {\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      padding: 10px 12px;\\n      vertical-align: top;\\n      text-align: left;\\n    }\\n    th {\\n      background: var(--head);\\n      font-weight: 650;\\n    }\\n    code {\\n      background: var(--code);\\n      border-radius: 4px;\\n      padding: 1px 5px;\\n      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, \\\"Liberation Mono\\\", monospace;\\n      font-size: 0.94em;\\n    }\\n    ul, ol {\\n      margin: 8px 0;\\n      padding-left: 22px;\\n    }\\n    li { margin: 5px 0; }\\n    .meta {\\n      color: var(--muted);\\n      font-size: 14px;\\n    }\\n    .cards {\\n      display: grid;\\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));\\n      gap: 12px;\\n      margin-top: 16px;\\n    }\\n    .card {\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\n      padding: 14px;\\n      background: #fbfcfe;\\n    }\\n    .card strong {\\n      display: block;\\n      color: var(--muted);\\n      font-size: 13px;\\n      font-weight: 600;\\n      margin-bottom: 6px;\\n    }\\n    .card span {\\n      display: block;\\n      font-size: 20px;\\n      font-weight: 760;\\n    }\\n    .bad { color: var(--red); }\\n    .warn { color: var(--amber); }\\n    .ok { color: var(--green); }\\n    .note {\\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);\\n      padding: 10px 12px;\\n      background: #eef5ff;\\n      border-radius: 4px;\\n      margin-top: 12px;\\n    }\\n    .note.warn {\\n      border-left-color: var(--amber);\\n      background: #fff5db;\\n    }\\n    .note.bad {\\n      border-left-color: var(--red);\\n      background: #fdeeee;\\n    }\\n    .tag {\\n      display: inline-block;\\n      border-radius: 999px;\\n      padding: 2px 8px;\\n      font-size: 12px;\\n      font-weight: 700;\\n      background: #eef2f7;\\n      color: #39445a;\\n      white-space: nowrap;\\n    }\\n    .tag.bad { background: #fdeeee; color: var(--red); }\\n    .tag.warn { background: #fff5db; color: var(--amber); }\\n    .tag.ok { background: #e9f7ef; color: var(--green); }\\n    .tag.info { background: #e7f0ff; color: var(--blue); }\\n    .small { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }\\n    a { color: var(--blue); }\\n    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\\n    .child-link {\\n      font-weight: 650;\\n      text-decoration: none;\\n      border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--blue);\\n    }\\n    @media (max-width: 900px) {\\n      main { padding: 24px 14px 42px; }\\n      .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\\n      table { font-size: 13px; }\\n      th, td { padding: 8px; }\\n    }\\n    @media (max-width: 560px) {\\n      .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\\n    }\\n  </style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n<main>\\n  <header>\\n    <h1>Body-Tell 与 VoxTell 论文不一致项总控计划</h1>\\n    <p class=\\\"meta\\\">日期：2026-05-24。范围：<code>VoxTell/VoxTell.pdf</code>、<code>VoxTell/</code> 官方实现/权重计划、当前 <code>Body-Tell/</code> 训练相关代码与配置。根目录 <code>train.py</code> 未纳入。</p>\\n    <div class=\\\"cards\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"card\\\"><strong>明确不一致</strong><span class=\\\"bad\\\">13 项</span></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"card\\\"><strong>已分发到子计划</strong><span class=\\\"ok\\\">13 项</span></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"card\\\"><strong>已起草子计划</strong><span class=\\\"ok\\\">3 个</span></div>\\n      <div class=\\\"card\\\"><strong>总体判断</strong><span class=\\\"warn\\\">可执行，待实施（2026-05-24 修订）</span></div>\\n    </div>\\n    <p class=\\\"note warn\\\">2026-05-24 修订：原 11 项基础上新增 #12 BCE+Dice loss 等价性、#13 <code>num_heads</code> mismatch（Body-Tell=32 vs VoxTell=1）。其中 #13 同时修正了原 SP-A 中\\\"VoxTell projection 输出 <code>[32,2048,4096,8192,10240]</code>\\\"的错误表述（实际为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320]</code> 量级，<code>num_heads</code> 才是根因）。</p>\\n    <div class=\\\"note warn\\\"><strong>域差异豁免（2026-05-24 重要约束）</strong>：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid，VoxTell 处理医学影像（CT/MRI/PET）。任务输入模态、特征统计、噪声特性都不同。<strong>本计划中\\\"对齐\\\"是手段不是目的，目的是支持 VoxTell 权重复用与实现一致性。任何一项不一致，若实现阶段 audit 后发现对齐会损害性能、或对当前任务没有可观察收益、或与权重复用无关，允许显式跳过并在子计划中记录原因。</strong> #12（loss 公式）与 #13（<code>num_heads</code>）尤其适用此豁免。</div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <section>\\n    <h2>使用方式</h2>\\n    <p>本文件是父级执行总控，只回答三件事：先做什么、每个差异由哪个子计划负责、什么时候可以进入下一阶段。代码级方案、测试命令和参数细节以三个子计划为准。</p>\\n    <p class=\\\"note\\\">域适配差异（输入模态、patch size、augmentation、global batch、数据/词表规模等）视为 Body-Tell 前提，不作为本轮整改目标。本轮只处理可在 Body-Tell 域内对齐的模型结构、数据构造和训练机制。</p>\\n  </section>\\n\\n  <section>\\n    <h2>子计划索引</h2>\\n    <table>\\n      <thead>\\n        <tr>\\n          <th>编号</th>\\n          <th>子计划</th>\\n          <th>关注范围</th>\\n          <th>状态</th>\\n        </tr>\\n      </thead>\\n      <tbody>\\n        <tr>\\n          <td>SP-A</td>\\n          <td><a class=\\\"child-link\\\" href=\\\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\\\">Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</a></td>\\n          <td>模型结构对齐：transformer decoder 语义、ResidualEncoder、VoxTellDecoder、5-scale projection、位置编码策略、VoxTell 权重加载入口、训练实验矩阵。</td>\\n          <td><span class=\\\"tag ok\\\">已起草</span></td>\\n        </tr>\\n        <tr>\\n          <td>SP-B</td>\\n          <td><a class=\\\"child-link\\\" href=\\\"bodytell_sampling_vocabulary_optimization_report.html\\\">Body-Tell Sampling 与 Vocabulary 优化思路</a></td>\\n          <td>数据构造对齐：动态采样基础设施、85% foreground patch oversampling、patch 内 2+1 prompt、25/75 canonical/variant、aggregate sampler、vocabulary expansion、text embedding 重建。</td>\\n          <td><span class=\\\"tag ok\\\">已起草</span></td>\\n        </tr>\\n        <tr>\\n          <td>SP-C</td>\\n          <td><a class=\\\"child-link\\\" href=\\\"bodytell_training_loop_eval_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\\\">Body-Tell 训练机制与评估协议对齐计划</a></td>\\n          <td>训练循环对齐：fixed-update epoch/iteration 节奏、SGD + polynomial decay、deep supervision 5-scale loss 权重、checkpoint/scheduler resume、prompt robustness / negative / held-out 评估协议、paper-aligned 测试矩阵。</td>\\n          <td><span class=\\\"tag ok\\\">已起草</span></td>\\n        </tr>\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_3\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"find Body-Tell -maxdepth 4 -type f | sort | sed -n '1,220p'\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"Body-Tell/artifacts/text_embeddings/prompt_embeddings.pt\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/dataset.py\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__init__.py\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/dataset.cpython-312.pyc\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/dataset.cpython-313.pyc\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/__init__.cpython-312.pyc\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/__init__.cpython-313.pyc\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/vocabulary.cpython-312.pyc\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/vocabulary.cpython-313.pyc\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/vocabulary.py\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/__init__.py\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/losses/__init__.py\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/los